of Survival、Massimiliano Paggliara 等人合作。</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dj-and-singer-songwriter-aerea-negrot-dies-aged-43-3515929">DJ 兼创作歌手 Aérea Negrot 去世，享年 43 岁，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
